{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/operation/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"SH"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"36e43edb-365c-54c9-b85b-c294336b688c","excerpt":"운영 장애 대응 인식 보고 롤백 복구 피드백 Postmortem 대응 후 회고 종료시점을 내가 통제하면 관리가 편해진다 uvicorn에 종료카운트랑 karpenter에 expireAfter가 있고, jwtToken 같은 보안쪽에도 만료시간이 정해져있다 DevOps vs SRE…","html":"<h2 id=\"운영\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%B4%EC%98%81\" aria-label=\"운영 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>운영</h2>\n<h4 id=\"장애-대응\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%A5%EC%95%A0-%EB%8C%80%EC%9D%91\" aria-label=\"장애 대응 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>장애 대응</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>인식</li>\n<li>보고</li>\n<li>롤백</li>\n<li>복구</li>\n<li>피드백</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"postmortem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#postmortem\" aria-label=\"postmortem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Postmortem</h4>\n<p>대응 후 회고</p>\n<h4 id=\"종료시점을-내가-통제하면-관리가-편해진다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A2%85%EB%A3%8C%EC%8B%9C%EC%A0%90%EC%9D%84-%EB%82%B4%EA%B0%80-%ED%86%B5%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B4-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%EA%B0%80-%ED%8E%B8%ED%95%B4%EC%A7%84%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"종료시점을 내가 통제하면 관리가 편해진다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>종료시점을 내가 통제하면 관리가 편해진다</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>uvicorn에 종료카운트랑</li>\n<li>karpenter에 expireAfter가 있고, jwtToken 같은 보안쪽에도 만료시간이 정해져있다</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"devops-vs-sre\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#devops-vs-sre\" aria-label=\"devops vs sre permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DevOps vs SRE</h4>\n<p>DevOps gonna make fast to deploy\nSRE gonna maintaining production to reliability</p>\n<h4 id=\"sre\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sre\" aria-label=\"sre permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SRE</h4>\n<p>To upgrade site reliability</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Monitoring\n<ul>\n<li>Monitoring various content</li>\n<li>Make automation</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Performance check</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Quick recovery scenario</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Check error 5xx, when error occurred rollback to prev version. And reporting\nerror situation. Which are link, behavior, data, code line, build package,\n(commit source)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"성과-측정과-개선\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%B1%EA%B3%BC-%EC%B8%A1%EC%A0%95%EA%B3%BC-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0\" aria-label=\"성과 측정과 개선 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>성과 측정과 개선</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>DevOps 성과 지표\n<ul>\n<li>DORA Metrics\n<ul>\n<li>Deployment Frequency</li>\n<li>Lead Time</li>\n<li>MTTR</li>\n<li>Change Failure Rate</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"edge-case\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#edge-case\" aria-label=\"edge case permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>edge case</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>로그 폭발</li>\n<li>권한 남용</li>\n<li>시스템 다운</li>\n<li>네트워크 혼잡</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"운영까지의-고려\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%B4%EC%98%81%EA%B9%8C%EC%A7%80%EC%9D%98-%EA%B3%A0%EB%A0%A4\" aria-label=\"운영까지의 고려 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>운영까지의 고려</h4>\n<p>되돌릴 수 있는가\n복구할 수 있는가\n관리할 사람을 구할 수 있는가\n버전관리</p>\n<h4 id=\"프로덕션에-필요한-속성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EB%8D%95%EC%85%98%EC%97%90-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"프로덕션에 필요한 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로덕션에 필요한 속성</h4>\n<p>보안, 개별 설정을 유연하게 하는 것, 관측성</p>\n<ul>\n<li>되돌릴 수 있는가</li>\n<li>복구할 수 있는가</li>\n<li>수습이 가능한가</li>\n<li>인수인계할 때 무리가 없는가 (사람을 구할 수 있는가)</li>\n<li>안정성</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"program\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#program\" aria-label=\"program permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Program</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>code with log, test, api</li>\n<li>CI with lint, test, performance, dependency</li>\n<li>CD with deploy</li>\n<li>Monitoring with check node, api, log, performance</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"need-extra-component\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#need-extra-component\" aria-label=\"need extra component permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Need Extra Component</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>M/L</li>\n<li>Elasticsearch</li>\n<li>[[Information#무질서한 원숭이(Chaos Monkey)]]</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"reboot-report\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reboot-report\" aria-label=\"reboot report permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>reboot report</h4>\n<p>load average 확인 후 cpu bound인지 memory bound인지 disk i/o문제인지 확인하는 것처럼\n문제 감지되면 확인된 기록들을 캡처해서 리포트로 보내주고 재부팅하도록 설정\n소프트웨어 로그, 시스템로그도 같이 캡처</p>\n<h4 id=\"구성보다-관습-coc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EB%B3%B4%EB%8B%A4-%EA%B4%80%EC%8A%B5-coc\" aria-label=\"구성보다 관습 coc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구성보다 관습, CoC</h4>\n<p>설정을 일일이 하기보다 관습적으로 따르게 하고, 설정이 필요할 때만 설정을 하는 방식</p>\n<p>같은 약자로 Code of Conduct(행동 규범)이 있어 헷갈릴 수 있다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"오토스케일링\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%A4%ED%86%A0%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%9D%BC%EB%A7%81\" aria-label=\"오토스케일링 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>오토스케일링</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>cpu나 메모리가 70% 이상이면 1대씩 늘리고 30% 미만이면 1대씩 줄이는 방식</li>\n<li>근데 cpu와 메모리가 한번에 100%가 되는 경우가 왕왕 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"대규모-서버에서-겪는-문제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8C%80%EA%B7%9C%EB%AA%A8-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EA%B2%AA%EB%8A%94-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"대규모 서버에서 겪는 문제 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>대규모 서버에서 겪는 문제</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>데이터 : 데이터의 동기화</li>\n<li>CPU : cpu 병목</li>\n<li>네트워크 : 네트워크 병목</li>\n</ul>\n<p>load average를 확인하고 sar을 통해 cpu 문제인지 io문제인지 확인한다</p>\n<h4 id=\"대용량-트래픽\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8C%80%EC%9A%A9%EB%9F%89-%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD\" aria-label=\"대용량 트래픽 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>대용량 트래픽</h4>\n<p>WAS에서 문제가 생길 때 다중화로 해결이 힘든 이유</p>\n<ul>\n<li>다른 WAS를 찾아야 한다.</li>\n<li>로그인 정보를 전달해줘야 한다. (세션 클러스터링 필요)\n<ul>\n<li>그에 따른 관리 지점 증가</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>데이터베이스 다중화 힘든 이유</p>\n<ul>\n<li>동기화</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"운영","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%EC%9A%B4%EC%98%81","ariaLabel":"운영 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"운영"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h4","properties":{"id":"장애-대응","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%EC%9E%A5%EC%95%A0-%EB%8C%80%EC%9D%91","ariaLabel":"장애 대응 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]